author: Iftikhar Firdous
title: Three Levies personnel killed in Mohmand Agency suicide attack
text:
Share Tweet Email 
At least three Levies personnel were killed on Wednesday as a suicide attacker blew himself in front of a political agent’s office in Mohmand Agency. 
“Two suicide bombers tried entering the compound of the political administration,” a senior official told The Express Tribune . 
Security forces foiled the terrorists’ attempt to enter an agency’s headquarters in the area and killed the suicide bomber at the main gate. 
-This is a developing story and will be updated accordingly
